&gt; Ragnar followed her as he could, but he was soon lagging behind as the
&gt; reactor in the mech he had morphed into produced only limited power
&gt; for movement.

Maxima glanced over her shoulder as she raced towards the destination. 
Smirking at the lagging &#39;bot&#39;.

&gt; 
&gt; He called at maximal base.
&gt; 
&gt; Ragnar: Base, this is Ragnar. I am escorting a &quot;guest&quot; that is coming
&gt; your way. She says she&#39;s a decepticon and she is quite... unpleasant.
&gt; Can someone welcome her, quiaff?
&gt; 
&gt; Blackfang received the message and replied.
&gt; 
&gt; Blackfang: Aff, Big Guy. Blackfang here, I&#39;ll greet her home. Over.
&gt; 
&gt; The wolf bot stood and went at the base&#39;s entrance. He would see her
&gt; when she showed up. Until then, shields were up.
&gt; 
&gt; 

With him lagging, she called out. &quot;What&#39;s wrong, Human? Cannot keep up with a 
REAL Transformer?&quot; 

She laughed as she raced on ahead. Enjoying the speed. It was one of her 
fancies anyway when she was a jet. She often liked to use it to push one of 
Starscream&#39;s buttons. 

Soon enough, she was within the range of the base. Her optics beheld the 
structure. &#39;So this is the pathetic place. Pathetic indeed.&#39; Her mind 
definitely came up with rebuilding her old form as well as setting off in 
search of the Ark. She had to. Only Teletran 1 could rebuild her completely. 
She doubted that anyone here would rebuild her the way SHE wanted to be. 

She noticed a wolf like bot awaiting & groaned as she slowed down & padded up 
to him. &quot;You must be the welcoming committee.&quot; her clear optics gazed at the 
wolf. 

